We accept game rules for the long-term only when they are immutable.  Like the laws of the universe... can't change those.. but Sony <i>can</i> and does change the rules of EQ quite a lot.  However, they are very reluctant to change some of the rules for fear of backlash from people who would, for good reason, say things like, &quot;this really cheapens the game... all that 'hard work' [translation: mousing and clicking] I had to go through to get grandmaster in jewelcrafting is now worthless.&quot;
