<br />
On the other hand, if McDonald's doesn't listen to their customer base and adapt, they will go out of business eventually because there probably will be competitors who do listen and adapt.   Some customers will stick with McDonald's out of loyalty, ignorance, habit, or because they truly prefer McDonald's products, but others will vote with their feet. 
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">
